---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Revenue Recovery + Growth Program — $2,500/mo | BrandsBuilders',
  description: 'One program. Two phases. First we recover $15–30k from your missed calls and old customer list — in 2 weeks, without ad spend. Then we build the system that brings new clients every month.',
  canonical: 'https://brandsbuilders.ca/services',
};
---

<Layout seo={seo}>

  <!-- Header -->
  <section class="bg-white pt-16 pb-14 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 border border-gray-200 text-gray-600 text-xs font-semibold mb-6">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 shrink-0 animate-pulse"></span>
        1 spot available this week
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-5">
        Revenue Recovery + Growth Program
      </h1>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">$2,500<span class="text-2xl text-gray-500 font-normal">/mo</span></span>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="bg-green-50 text-green-700 border border-green-200 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">No setup fee</span>
          <span class="bg-green-50 text-green-700 border border-green-200 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">No contract</span>
          <span class="bg-orange-50 text-orange-700 border border-orange-200 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Guaranteed results</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
        In your missed calls and old customer list there's $15–30k a year sitting on the floor. We recover it in the first 2 weeks — and that pays for the system that brings new clients every month.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/apply" class="inline-flex px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white bg-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-800 transition">
          Apply now →
        </a>
        <a href="https://cal.com/brandsbuilders/30-min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex px-8 py-3.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 border border-gray-300 hover:border-gray-400 transition">
          Talk first
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ GUARANTEE ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-14">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-orange-400 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">The Guarantee</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">
            If we don't generate more in booked jobs than you paid us in 30 days — we work free until we do.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed text-sm">
            All the risk is on us. If the system doesn't work, you don't pay more until it does. No arguments, no fine print.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl p-6 space-y-4">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">How it's measured</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">Booked jobs attributed to the system — calls and texts through the tracked number + reactivation replies — with estimated value over $2,500 in the month. All visible in your dashboard.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-t border-gray-700 pt-4">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Your only part of the deal</p>
            <ul class="space-y-1.5">
              <li class="text-sm text-gray-300 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">✓</span> You return leads within 24 hours</li>
              <li class="text-sm text-gray-300 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">✓</span> You give us access in week 1</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ ROADMAP ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">The roadmap</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 text-lg">What happens each week from day one</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 1 -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-orange-200"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-orange-600 uppercase tracking-wider bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Phase 1 — Recovery</span>
          <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-orange-200"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          {[
            { when: 'Week 1', win: 'You\'ll know exactly how much money is leaking', how: 'Full funnel audit + tracked number installation + dashboard. Missed-Call Recovery live in 48 hours: every missed call gets an automatic text back within seconds.' },
            { when: 'Week 2', win: 'First jobs booked — without spending on ads', how: 'Reactivation campaign to your base: unclosed estimates, customers from 1–2 years ago. Automated follow-up on new incoming leads.' },
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="border border-orange-200 bg-orange-50 rounded-xl p-6">
              <div class="text-xs font-bold text-orange-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">{item.when}</div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">{item.win}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">{item.how}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2 -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gray-200"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-wider bg-gray-100 border border-gray-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Phase 2 — Growth</span>
          <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gray-200"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          {[
            { when: 'Week 3', win: 'Your site ready to convert', how: 'Landing page / website optimization + end-to-end analytics with full sales attribution.' },
            { when: 'Week 4', win: 'Campaign live', how: 'Full campaign setup + creatives + launch. First qualified leads coming in.' },
            { when: 'Month 2', win: 'Real ROI vs. your baseline', how: 'Actual sales results. Creatives and landing improving week over week, not stagnating.' },
            { when: 'Month 3+', win: 'We scale what works', how: 'Budget scaling based on your unit economics. Quarterly action plan with 3 months of your real data.' },
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-5">
              <div class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">{item.when}</div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm mb-2">{item.win}</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">{item.how}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ INCLUDES ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 border-y border-gray-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What your fee covers</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6">The $2,500 includes all our work — no upsells, no surprises.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            {[
              'Missed-call recovery system (tracked number + auto-SMS 24/7)',
              'Reactivation campaigns (SMS + email to your customer list)',
              'Full ads management (Google or Meta) — creatives included',
              'Landing page / website optimization',
              'End-to-end tracking and reporting',
              'Dashboard with every lead and its source',
              'Direct access to me — response under 24h',
            ].map(item => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What goes separately</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6">Ad spend — straight from your card to Google/Meta.</p>
          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-500" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 14.5v-9l6 4.5-6 4.5z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 text-sm">Ad budget — in accounts you own</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-0.5">Recommended $1,500–2,500/mo when we start phase 2. We don't touch that money or mark it up.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-4 text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
              If you ever leave, the ad accounts and all data stay with you. No lock-in.
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-5 bg-orange-50 border border-orange-200 rounded-xl p-5 text-sm text-orange-900 leading-relaxed">
            <strong>The first 2–4 weeks you spend nothing on ads.</strong> The recovery phase works on what you already have. The goal: ad spend gets paid for by what phase 1 already generated.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ TIME INVESTMENT ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-white py-14">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Your time investment</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-8">
        ~3 hours during initial setup for access and feedback. After that, ~1 hour a month to review reporting. The point of the system is that it works without you on top of it.
      </p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">~3 hours</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Initial setup</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">~1 hour</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Per month reviewing results</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-600">&lt; 24h</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Our response time to you</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ FINAL CTA ═══ -->
  <section class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-16 text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3">Does your business qualify?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 text-lg">We only work with trades doing $1M–$3M in revenue. If that's you, apply now — 1 spot available this week.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/apply" class="inline-flex px-9 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 transition text-lg">
          Apply now →
        </a>
        <a href="https://cal.com/brandsbuilders/30-min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex px-9 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white border border-gray-700 hover:border-gray-500 transition text-lg">
          Talk first
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
